target.sql_fulltext: with J as -- 35069142 => 0 (select /*+ materialize */ min(object_id), object_type from dba_objects where object_name like '%J%' group by object_type ), L as ( select /*+ materialize */ min(object_id), object_type from dba_objects where object_name like '%L%' group by object_type ), M as ( select /*+ materialize */ min(object_id), object_type from dba_objects where object_name like '%M%' group by object_type ) select /*+ MONITOR */ * from l,j,m
